<note><title>5、数据表创建/删除</title><content><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">（1）创建数据表</span></font></div><hr /><ul><li><div>创建数据表：CREATE TABLE [IF NOT EXISTS] table_name(column_name data_type,...);</div></li></ul><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14902);-en-codeblock:true;"><div>mysql&gt; create database t1;<br /></div><div>Query OK, 1 row affected (0.01 sec)</div><div><br /></div><div>mysql&gt; use t1;</div><div>Database changed</div><div>mysql&gt; create table tb1(</div><div>    -&gt; username varchar(20),</div><div>    -&gt; age tinyint unsigned,</div><div>    -&gt; salary float(8,2) unsigned</div><div>    -&gt; );</div><div>Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.04 sec)</div></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">（2）查看数据表</span></div><hr /><ul><li><div>查看数据库中的数据表：SHOW TABLES [ FROM mysql ];</div></li></ul><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14902);-en-codeblock:true;"><div>mysql&gt; <font color="#FF2600">show tables;</font></div><div>+--------------+</div><div>| Tables_in_t1 |</div><div>+--------------+</div><div>| tb1          |</div><div>+--------------+</div><div>1 row in set (0.00 sec)</div><div><br /></div><div>mysql&gt; <font color="#FF2600">show tables from mysql;</font></div><div>+---------------------------+</div><div>| Tables_in_mysql           |</div><div>+---------------------------+</div><div>| columns_priv              |</div><div>| component                 |</div><div>| db                        |</div><div>| user                      |</div><div>+---------------------------+</div><div>33 rows in set (0.00 sec)</div></div><ul><li><div>查看数据表结构：SHOW COLUMNS FROM tb_name;</div></li></ul><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14902);-en-codeblock:true;"><div>mysql&gt; <font color="#FF2600">show columns from tb1;</font></div><div>+----------+---------------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</div><div>| Field    | Type                | Null | Key | Default | Extra |</div><div>+----------+---------------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</div><div>| username | varchar(20)         | YES  |     | NULL    |       |</div><div>| age      | tinyint(3) unsigned | YES  |     | NULL    |       |</div><div>| salary   | float(8,2) unsigned | YES  |     | NULL    |       |</div><div>+----------+---------------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</div><div>3 rows in set (0.00 sec)</div></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">（3）删除数据表</span></div><hr /><ul><li><div>删除数据表：drop table [if exists] table_name;</div></li></ul><div style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(251, 250, 248); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14902);-en-codeblock:true;"><div>mysql&gt; drop table tb1;<br /></div><div>Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.05 sec)</div><div><br /></div><div>mysql&gt; drop table tb1;</div><div>ERROR 1051 (42S02): Unknown table 't1.tb1'</div><div>mysql&gt; <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 250, 165);-evernote-highlight:true;">drop table if exists tb1;</span></div><div>Query OK, 0 rows affected, 1 warning (0.00 sec)</div></div></div><div><br /></div></en-note>]]></content><created>20170214T084558Z</created><updated>20181117T140440Z</updated><note-attributes><author>372251027@qq.com</author><source>desktop.win</source><source-application>evernote.win32</source-application><reminder-order>0</reminder-order></note-attributes></note>
